Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:13.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「君が許さなかった世界はこんなにも綺麗だ」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:19.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「悲しみを生むこと、全てが悪だとでも言うのか？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現実の銃口　突きつけた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:24.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}矜持たちが　壊れても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}僕は僕でしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:34.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Against the gunpoint, ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I'll rise like the break dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I save them for the final day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dream of the world for me and "fantasia"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.09,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It's time to go...Unshaken mind!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}揺れる視界を薙ぎ払い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:01.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愛すべき"正義"を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:07.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}語られない明日のために生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儚さと　痛みの中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}狂気だけが走らせる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全てが還る日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:20.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I face out, hold out to world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:13.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「你所不原谅的世界是这样美丽」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:19.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「制造悲伤的一切都是邪恶吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现实的枪口已指向了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:24.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使矜持悉数破碎崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也仍然只是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:34.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迎着枪口 随时准备战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会像破晓的黎明那样喷薄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我为末日将他们拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向往着为我与幻想而存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是时候启程了…怀着坚定的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去改变世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}清空动摇的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:01.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寻找值得热爱的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:07.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为无从诉说的明天而生存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在虚幻与痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:12.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有疯狂在穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在一切回归之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:20.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我将勇敢地面对世界
